{"tid":1404251,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"設路障係阻止警察速龍推進捉人， 比前線都有機會走到， 唔係畀你哋死守搏拉呀","createTime":"2019-08-04T03:36:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T20:18:49.000Z","uid":43785,"like":49,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e1cf956610f8927032998cec7bfc48c935b6a32c","tid":1404251,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T03:36:44.000Z","msg":"設路障係阻止警察速龍推進捉人， 後面要退，同時比前線都有機會走到， 唔係畀你哋死守搏拉呀。<br />\n<br />\n有幾點你哋係需要記住<br />\n第一，你哋班後生仔嘅裝備只不過係用嚟防守， 你哋冇本事進攻。<br />\n第二，你哋打唔過人地，人地有槍， 有專業訓練。<br />\n第三， 我唔想再有前線作無謂嘅死守犧牲。<br />\n第四， 唔好有種感覺係覺得叫走就係散水， 係懦弱嘅行為， 走都係一種勇氣架。<br />\n<br />\n記住呀你哋嘅裝備只不過係令你哋對線期間減少所受到嘅傷害並，唔係打贏佢哋嘅裝備。"},{"pid":"44d9c0170b1885d1bc967aacc09d34ca8e1b032d","tid":1404251,"uid":51848,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T03:36:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FERnLGX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFERnLGX.png&h=5bae3a07&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"256f48daffe0662b106802f95a7271bd0327dcf9","tid":1404251,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T03:40:56.000Z","msg":"各位， 好好諗下抗爭 我哋嘅長處同短處， 唔好畀人拉， 我望見前線係企喺度畀人拉好心痛"},{"pid":"c6e1cc1e5ab8f56656c4470bd3a4c2c10efc109d","tid":1404251,"uid":264724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T03:42:10.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"47b028b1a0a81c92b0e70cecf21f3f5270765737","tid":1404251,"uid":264724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T03:42:25.000Z","msg":"強帖"},{"pid":"0f663c677d3a12c81cd3a1effc3f27b1e24fb786","tid":1404251,"uid":264724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T03:42:35.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"1e0c8e407f03942b51bdf2fbe0b04b18a2fc74f2","tid":1404251,"uid":264724,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T03:43:12.000Z","msg":"我以後打算著街坊裝踢拖去遊行"},{"pid":"5ae06bd08b4888baf6db7de912a5cd5aeb5867f2","tid":1404251,"uid":264724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":